[Modal is opened]
If the modal has not [no-backdrop], when the user clicks outside of the modal
When the user clicks on <button.close-modal>
  A 'close' event is emitted
  Wait 200ms
  The modal is not visible

When the modal is not opened
  The modal is not visible

[On mobile]
When the modal is opened
  A <button.close-modal> is shown

If the modal has not [close-button] or has [title]
  The modal contains <.modal-wrapper .header>
